title: FGC: Virtual Boy ROMs - No-Intro 2012-02-06

Full Game Collections: Virtual Boy
==================================

This torrent is intended for sharing the full collection of Virtual Boy roms,
compiled to match the No-Intro[1] database, dated 2012-02-06.
